name: Schizoid Bunny #17
description:
Puppet: -Wait a minute. You're telling me I'm a puppet?
Schizoid Bunny #17: -Exactly. I'm giving you the word and the intention.
Puppet: -Are you sure? I can feel life coursing through my veins, it's so real.
SB#17: -Don't be fooled by your senses, perception is not always true to reality. Even most of our life is also an illusion, it's just that from this perspective we find it impossible to accept it.
Puppet: -Oh shit, you're scaring me! You're a crazy liar, I'm as real as these ficking bunnies floating around us!
SB#17: -What bunnies? There are only two of us here, and you're definitely the one who's crazy.
